import mdtraj as md

"""
Print version string
"""
print(md.version.full_version)
# end

'''
Render a picture of lysozyme protein with nglview

1. import packages
2. Download 1GWD protein
3. Render it
4. Embed in jupyter notebook
'''

# import packages
import nglview as nv
import mdtraj as md

# Download 1GWD protein
t = md.load(nv.datafiles.GRO)

# Render it
view = nv.show_mdtraj(t)
view

# Embed in jupyter notebook
view._display_image()
